    "Previous studies concentrate on augmenting the decompiler output's variable names and types.",
    "Considering the situations of realistic reverse engineering, proper comments describing the purposes of the code snippets and easy-to-read code style will also boost the experience of analyzing binaries.",
    "Moreover, previous methods tend to handle only one or two optimization types.",
